Judy M. Poferl



Ms. Judy M. Poferl is Secretary, Senior VP & Head-Executive Services at Xcel Energy, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Minnesota Chamber of Commerce, The Science Museum of Minnesota, Greater Twin Cities United Way, Minneapolis Downtown Council, College of Saint Benedict, and Minnesota Women's Economic Roundtable, Inc.
Ms. Poferl was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Northern States Power Co., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Northern States Power Co., and a Principal by CenterPoint Energy Resources Corp.
She received her undergraduate degree from the College of Saint Benedict and a graduate degree from the Humphrey School of Public Affairs.



